data.description: Welcome to this charming but modern 3 bedroom, 2 bath home nestled in the heart of Winter Haven. In 5 minutes you can be in downtown enjoying a festival in the park, crafted cocktails, a lavish dinner, or gourmet baked goods. This city has it all. The home was completely updated in 2019 with a new architectural roof, windows and doors, upgraded bathrooms, new water heater and electrical panel, and beautiful tile floors. There are 2 large sheds in the rear of the large fenced backyard . One actually has a window unit ready to be someone’s workshop or she shed. The highlight of the home is the gorgeous modern kitchen with stainless appliances that opens up right into the spacious living area with an impressive statement wall. It has a classic split plan that parents love and a private bathroom in the master suite. This home has too much to offer to last long. Don’t hesitate! Schedule your private showing today!
